### User Tests ###

### Get user
GET {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1
Accept: application/json

### Get user bookmarks
GET {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/bookmarks
Accept: application/json

### Get user bookmark by pageID
GET {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/bookmarks/30855
Accept: application/json

### POST user bookmark
POST {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer {{Authentication_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "PageId": "30855"
}

### DELETE user bookmark
DELETE {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/bookmarks/30855
Authorization: Bearer {{Authentication_Token}}

### Get user ratings
GET {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/ratings
Accept: application/json

### Get user rating by TitleID
GET {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/ratings/tt13652970
Accept: application/json

### POST user rating
POST {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/ratings
Authorization: Bearer {{Authentication_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TitleId": "tt13652970",
  "Rating": 10,
  "ReviewText": "Great movie!"
}

### PUT user rating (update existing)
PUT {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/ratings/tt13652970
Authorization: Bearer {{Authentication_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Rating": 9,
  "ReviewText": "Actually, I think it's a 9."
}

### DELETE user rating
DELETE {{WebService_HostAddress}}/api/v2/users/1/ratings/tt13652970
Authorization: Bearer {{Authentication_Token}}

